chunk_content: For children reported as “Reported HIV-Positive - not currently on ART or ART Status Unknown,” what efforts are being undertaken in response? Are there certain partners with low ART coverage, why? Is this an issue related to community case management? Or are partners unable to collect timely confirmation of treatment status (i.e., missing)?
